name: 0-800-ANGER-00
description:
I'm trying to heal inside but everytime I go to bed, this feeling called anger makes me explode. And I feel embarrassed because I'm supposed to feel love and good things after all this time. Then, I understood that anger is not a bad or a good feeling, is just an emotion. Emotions are necessary to do things. Feelings are neutral. And I need the anger and the darkness to met the love and happiness.

I always feel too much. I am intense. And I want to show you in a self-portrait. I want to express my feelings, I want to show the universe inside me through photography.
